        <p>Currently, <em>Code with me</em> will not co-brand its workshops.</p>
        <p>To help us avoid conflicts of interest when pursuing our <a href="about.html">mission statement</a>, sponsors will not be involved in the application process or mentor selection. Employees of sponsoring organizations will not be given special consideration.</p>
